{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eventually, we will eat those potatoes until the next distribution.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, it was nighttime again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was all the stories-- all the stories again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and after these meals, you know, if-- many girls, they try to go to the kitchens to steal something, you know, to eat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many, they enter, and you know, they're more clever or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the more you know-- not clever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You must say they were, and they were starving the most.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] If they find you pinching a potato, or a piece of bread, or whatever, or an onion, whatever, they-- and they were to find you-- and it was very much punishment.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They will-- they will kill you on the spot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And beside that, you know, there were other punishment they could do to you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were-- especially, there were, you know, those dogs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was those dogs in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were very huge dogs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were afraid of those dogs more than the-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because they were train to make, you know, to make like sex with girls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if they want to punish you, they will take these horrible, big dogs, and they force you there to make whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In any case, one day, it happened there was a-- a-- a French lady.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had a beautiful daughter of 16.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was really beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, you know, they-- they-- they forced her, the girl-- I don't know what she has done wrong-- to do that with the dog.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The mother was-- was watching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- the girl died, because the dog was vicious, and bad, and big, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She die on the spot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the mother, she couldn't stand it anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She went and hanged herself to the barbed wire, you know, electric.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
